signature: default String lookup(final String key, final U object)
name: lookup
javadoc:
/**
 * Performs a lookup operation on the given object using the specified key.
 *
 * @param key   the key to perform the lookup with
 * @param object the object to perform the lookup on
 * @return      the result of the lookup operation, or null if not found
 */
improved_javadoc:
/**
 * Performs a lookup operation on the given object using the specified key.
 *
 * This method delegates to another lookup method with only the key as an argument. It does not perform any actual lookup
 * and will return null if the other lookup method returns null.
 *
 * @param key   the key to perform the lookup with
 * @param object the object to perform the lookup on (this parameter is ignored)
 * @return      the result of the lookup operation, or null if not found
 */
